      "writtenOn": "2020-08-11T16:06:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Here (and elsewhere) we should avoid mixing SkUnicode and the term \u0027icu\u0027. In fact outside the implementation of SkUnicode backed by ICU we should strongly avoid the term \u0027icu\u0027. This should probably just be named \u0027unicode\u0027.",
